    "content": "<p>Page one of Google gets 92% of all search traffic. If your Detroit business isn't there for your key terms, you're essentially invisible. The good news: for local Detroit searches, page one is absolutely achievable.</p><h2>Win the Map Pack</h2><p>The three business listings at the top of local search results get the most clicks. Winning here requires: a fully complete and verified GBP, the right primary category, 20+ high-quality photos, weekly posts, and a consistent stream of genuine Google reviews. Respond to every review within 24 hours.</p><h2>Win Organic Results</h2><p>Identify 3–5 primary search terms your customers actually use. For each term, create a dedicated page targeting it in the title, H1, and content. Include location-specific details. Add schema markup. Build backlinks from local directories and partner sites.</p><h2>Realistic Timelines</h2><p>Brand new website: 6–12 months for competitive terms. Existing site with proper optimization: 3–6 months. Specific local long-tail terms: sometimes weeks. Caliber manages this entire process for Growth and Scale clients. <a href='/#services'>Explore our SEO services</a> or <a href='/#contact'>get a free ranking assessment.</a></p>"
