    "content": "<p>Your Google Business Profile (GBP) is the most important free marketing tool available to Detroit small businesses. Fully optimized profiles receive 7x more clicks than incomplete ones. Most Detroit businesses are leaving massive traffic on the table.</p><h2>The Complete GBP Optimization Checklist</h2><ul><li>Business name (exact legal name — no keyword stuffing)</li><li>Primary category (most specific option that fits)</li><li>Up to 9 additional categories</li><li>Complete address or service area</li><li>Local phone number and website URL</li><li>Full business hours including holidays</li><li>750-character keyword-rich business description</li><li>Every service listed with descriptions</li><li>20+ high-quality photos (interior, exterior, team, work samples)</li><li>Weekly Google Posts with offers, events, or news</li><li>Q&amp;A section proactively populated</li><li>Reviews requested consistently, every review responded to within 24 hours</li></ul><p>Caliber Web Studio manages our clients' GBP as part of every plan. <a href='/#contact'>Let us audit your current GBP</a> or <a href='/#pricing'>see our plans with full GBP management.</a></p>"
