    "slug": "how-to-get-more-google-reviews",
    "title": "How to Get More Google Reviews for Your Detroit Business",
    "description": "Google reviews are one of the strongest local SEO signals. Here's a proven system for getting more 5-star reviews for your Detroit small business — without begging.",
    "date": "2025-06-25",
